### `POST /webhook-test/n8n/thermal`
Callback dari n8n setelah memproses data **thermal**. Path-prefix `/webhook-test/n8n/*` sengaja terpisah dari `/api/n8n/*` supaya jelas: ini endpoint **dipanggil oleh n8n** (server jadi *receiver*), bukan endpoint untuk client.

**Flow lengkap (round-trip)**
```
[ESP32] ‚Üí POST /api/sensor/ingest                          ‚ëÝ inbound
        ‚Üì                                                 (server simpan ke thermal_logs)
[Server] ‚Üí POST $N8N_THERMAL_WEBHOOK_URL                   ‚ë° outbound (fire-and-forget)
         payload includes insert_id + callback_url
        ‚Üì
[n8n] proses (AI / rule engine / Gemini)
        ‚Üì
[n8n] ‚Üí POST /webhook-test/n8n/thermal                     ‚ë¢ inbound (callback)
         body.source_id = insert_id dari thermal_logs
        ‚Üì                                                 (server simpan ke mitigation_logs
[Server] balas 201                                          dengan event_id=`THERMAL_${source_id}`)
```

**Request Body** (`application/json`) ‚Äî **fleksibel** (`additionalProperties: true`)

| Field | Tipe | Required | Default | Keterangan |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `source_id` | string | **Yes** | ‚Äî | Referensi `insert_id` dari `thermal_logs`. n8n wajib echo balik nilai `insert_id` yang diterima di outbound webhook (step ‚ë°). |
| `mitigation_advice` | string | No | `"(no advice provided by n8n)"` | Hasil olahan AI / rule engine |
| `confidence_score` | number 0‚Äì1 | No | `1.0` | Skor keyakinan AI |
| `raw_response` | object | No | `{}` | Raw response dari AI/Gemini |
| `metadata` | object | No | ‚Äî | Metadata bebas |
| _field tambahan_ | apa saja | ‚Äî | ‚Äî | Akan tetap masuk ke kolom `raw_response` di DB (full body di-spread). |

Contoh body minimal:
```json
{
  "mitigation_advice": "Aktifkan AC zona A, suhu di atas threshold 33¬∞C selama 15 menit",
  "confidence_score": 0.92
}
```

Contoh body lengkap:
```json
{
  "mitigation_advice": "...",
  "confidence_score": 0.88,
  "raw_response": {
    "model": "gemini-2.0-flash",
    "reasoning": "...",
    "tokens": 1024
  },
  "metadata": {
    "workflow_id": "thermal-mitigation-v3",
    "n8n_execution_id": "abc123"
  }
}
```

**Response `201`**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Thermal callback recorded.",
  "source_id": "42",
  "event_id": "THERMAL_42",
  "event_type": "thermal_anomaly",
  "insert_id": 105
}
```

**Response `400`** ‚Äî `source_id` kosong / `confidence_score` di luar range 0‚Äì1 / validasi JSON schema gagal.

**Response `500`** ‚Äî Kegagalan insert ke `mitigation_logs`.

**Penyimpanan di DB** ‚Äî record disimpan ke `mitigation_logs` dengan:
- `event_id` = `"THERMAL_${source_id}"` (mis. `THERMAL_42`)
- `event_type` = `"thermal_anomaly"` (hardcoded)
- `raw_response` = `JSON.stringify({ ...full_body, _source_id, _callback: 'thermal' })

