### `POST /webhook-test/n8n/earthquake`
Callback dari n8n setelah memproses data **gempa**. Mirror struktur dari endpoint thermal di atas, tapi `event_type` di-hardcode `earthquake`.

**Flow lengkap (round-trip)**
```
[BMKG poller] tarik autogempa.json tiap 60s                ‚ëÝ internal
        ‚Üì                                                 (server simpan ke earthquake_logs)
[Server] ‚Üí POST $N8N_GEMPA_WEBHOOK_URL                     ‚ë° outbound (fire-and-forget)
         payload includes insert_id + quake_id + callback_url
        ‚Üì
[n8n] proses (analisa magnitudo / jarak ke datacenter / dll)
        ‚Üì
[n8n] ‚Üí POST /webhook-test/n8n/earthquake                 ‚ë¢ inbound (callback)
         body.source_id = insert_id dari earthquake_logs
        ‚Üì                                                 (server simpan ke mitigation_logs
[Server] balas 201                                          dengan event_id=`EARTHQUAKE_${source_id}`)
```

**Request Body** ‚Äî **identik** dengan `/webhook-test/n8n/thermal` (schema sama, `additionalProperties: true`, `source_id` required).

**Response `201`**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
